name: rulf-the-adventure-webgame
description: Rulf is a platformer browsergame. The game has been designed and developed by Jeroen Vanhaeverbeke and Bastiaan Andriessen and is a school assignment for Devine (devine.be) at University College Howest in Kortrijk, Belgium.
author: Bastiaan Andriessen & Jeroen Vanhaeverbeke
